bio: Commercial artist. Apparel specialist. Brand designer. Family man. Owner of @chompbrand. No DM inquiries. Plz email! Portfolio site 👇🏽

social_posts.post_text:
We made it! @chompbrand on @arielhelwani’s MMA hour. I’m huge fan of this show. Thx for the shoutout dude! 

(He broke massive news today)

SWIPE. Fav projects from 2022. Love my clients. Hit me if you’re looking for brand design, illustration or apparel work.
.
#illustration #designinspo #digitalart #commercialart
Rush job for my friends at @kotaenergygroup. Custom art etched into a hatchet. A gift for their team to commemorate a trip to Wyoming. Fun, fast project.
I was interviewed for the final issue of @ironandair. Special shout-out to @mondo who encouraged me to start a brand 8 years ago.
EIGHT YEARS IN BIZ! A few of my fav moments and products from the last (nearly) decade. Thx to everyone who bought, supported or tattooed chomp. We’re still here!
Designed some boards for an @almondsurfboards x @chompbrand. The fish is for sale for $5 raffle. 20% of proceeds go to @awalkonwater.

Popped by the @fjallravenofficial shop to see the gift card boxes I designed. They’re little Kanken backpacks! Ended up grabbing some gear too!
.
#illustration #giftbox #designinspo

Designed a cute lil Jaws print for @rsvlts.
.
#rsvlts #swimtrunks #illustration #designinspo #youregonnaneedabiggerboat
I designed a beer can for @offshootbeerco. The beer of choice for coaches names Gordon Bombay.
“Live every week, like it was shark week” designed some sunnies for @knockaround’s Shark Week collaboration.

It’s my birthday! I started chomp 8.5 years ago before I had kids.  I wrote a kids book for all the rad dads and hot moms to read to their lil ones. Arrives next month! Use promo “ilovejoshsomuch” for 20% anything in the shop.
Quick identity design and trims package for the fine folks at @missionoutdoorclothing. Fun stuff.
SUMMER RECAP. Beach days, friend hangs, coastal excursions. Back to reality.
Lil Godzilla illustrations for @rsvlts. So cute. So scary.
Thanks a million to everyone the came by the Chomp booth at #adobemax. Loved meeting so many new people.
